DiscourseDB Core Model 0.5 API

Packages 
Package Description
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.configuration
Provides all configuration classes - in particular the Spring JavaConfig
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model
Contains the DiscourseDB Core object model with the object relational mappings using Hibernate 4.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.annotation
Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB Annotation Layer
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.macro
Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB Macro Layer
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.system
Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB System Layer
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.user
Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB User Layer
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.user.projection
Contains Spring Data Projections that constitute alternative views on existing entities.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository
Provides Spring Data Repository classes for the DiscourseDB Core entities provided in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.annotation
Contains Spring Data Repository classes for the DiscourseDB Annotation Layer entities provided in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.annotation.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.macro
Contains Spring Data Repository classes for the DiscourseDB Macro Layer entities provided in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.macro.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.system
Contains Spring Data Repository classes for the DiscourseDB System Layer entities provided in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.system.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.user
Contains Spring Data Repository classes for the DiscourseDB User Layer entities provided in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.user.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.annotation
Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB annotation repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.annotation.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.macro
Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB macro repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.macro.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.system
Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB system repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.system.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.user
Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB user repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.user.
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.type
This package holds enums for recurring types used in DiscourseDB.
